# TigerGate CNAPP Target Simulator – .gitignore
# ============================================================
# IMPORTANT: This project intentionally contains simulated
# secrets in plaintext (secrets/, cspm/, ciem/). Those are
# dummy/test values and are MEANT to be committed for
# security scanner testing. The real credentials in your
# environment should NEVER be committed.
# ============================================================

# Node.js
node_modules/
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
.npm
package-lock.json.bak

# Python
